-- U.K. Pledges Faster Review of Support for Renewable Electricity Projects
-- B y   S t e p h e n   C u n n i n g h a m
-- 2010-12-08T13:10:30Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-08/u-k-pledges-faster-review-of-support-for-renewable-electricity-projects.html
U.K. developers of large-scale
renewable electricity projects will get earlier indications
about how much support they will receive under the Renewables
Obligation from 2013, Energy Minister Charles Hendry said today
in a statement.  They will now find out how much support they will receive
as early as mid-July 2011, from a previous estimate of Autumn
2012.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Stephen Cunningham at 
 scunningha10@bloomberg.net  